short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects PoE Fandom requests to PoE Wiki, as well as removes PoE Fandom search results from Google.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects PoE Fandom (pathofexile.fandom.com) requests to PoE Wiki (poewiki.net) and adds an option to remove PoE Fandom search results from Google search results.
